1
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:17,840
Ai Xia

2
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:19,240
Sang Tuo

3
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,280
Fang Xiaomeng

4
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:23,080
I killed them all.

5
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:26,600
This...

6
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:29,320
This is God's will.

7
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:37,680
Chief.

8
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:40,760
Su Nian has fully confessed

9
00:01:40,760 --> 00:01:41,440
to the facts of the crime.

10
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:43,320
But given Su Nian's physical condition,

11
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,280
it's simply impossible

12
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,760
for her to commit these serial murders alone.

13
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:49,520
I suspect she has an accomplice.

14
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:52,400
Stop causing trouble for me, okay?

15
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:04,640
I used AI software

16
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:06,000
to generate footage of Anna

17
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,200
being sexually assaulted in prison.

18
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:09,440
If we add this video to our clip,

19
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:10,760
it will absolutely blow up.

20
00:02:10,760 --> 00:02:11,760
The traffic will be insane.

21
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,000
Shen Man, you...

22
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:18,000
I don't want that kind of traffic.

23
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,320
To speak for those whom life

24
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,840
has forced into the shadows.

25
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:24,480
That is why I made this video.

26
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:43,840
This is also why I created

27
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,640
this account for Shen Qing.

28
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:54,840
You've always loved being pretty.

29
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:32,880
Ah Zhu.

30
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,320
Come here a second.

31
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:40,080
Take these photos of Anna

32
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,200
and put them in the video.

33
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:43,680
I hope everyone remembers her beauty.

34
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:30,000
Thank you for speaking up.

35
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,120
Society needs more voices like this.

36
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:33,400
Reveal the truth.

37
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:34,480
Support justice.

38
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:44,960
Are you free?

39
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:49,360
I am.

40
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:02,680
So you knew

41
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:04,640
that Shen Qing was at a large religious gathering

42
00:05:04,640 --> 00:05:05,720
where she met Ai Xia.

43
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,880
That's why you went to find her.

44
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:10,160
That's right.

45
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,960
But the people at that gathering

46
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:14,040
seem to have nothing to do

47
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,600
with my sister's death.

48
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,400
What exactly happened back then?

49
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:19,160
Was there an autopsy for Shen Qing?

50
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:22,960
At the time, the police

51
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:24,600
only conducted a preliminary autopsy.

52
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:26,520
After ruling it a suicide,

53
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,280
they hastily closed the case.

54
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:33,720
She was obsessed with studying all kinds of esoteric arts.

55
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:36,640
That's also why she came to Tuo City.

56
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:38,280
This is what she left behind.

57
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,720
So that's why you make videos debunking things,

58
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:52,160
because you suspect

59
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:55,000
Shen Qing's death is related to esoteric arts.

60
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:57,760
I've tried everything I could think of,

61
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,440
but I still can't find any clues.

62
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:02,720
So I started making videos

63
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:04,080
while searching for clues.

64
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:06,320
It wasn't until I received Su Nian's card

65
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:08,960
that I found another clue related to Shen Qing.

66
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:10,960
You said it before.

67
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:12,680
This case isn't over.

68
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:14,160
If we keep investigating it,

69
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:16,400
we might find clues about Shen Qing.

70
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:23,440
Anna's case made me realize

71
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,400
that if you want to change people's attitudes,

72
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:26,760
just bringing the killer to justice

73
00:06:26,760 --> 00:06:27,760
is far from enough.

74
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:29,840
You also have to rely on the power of public opinion.

75
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,400
I want to team up with you

76
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,080
to continue investigating the case.

77
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:37,920
Okay.

78
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:40,640
That way, I can

79
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:42,280
continue investigating the cause of Shen Qing's death.

80
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:50,040
Hello?

81
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:50,960
Jiang Li.

82
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:53,080
There's been an incident at the Golden Elephant Casino on Beisha Road.

83
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:57,440
He...

84
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:57,960
Don't be scared. Don't be scared.

85
00:06:57,960 --> 00:06:58,640
He's the one who called the police.

86
00:06:58,640 --> 00:06:59,520
They won't come after you.

87
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:00,400
Don't be scared.

88
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,320
What was the situation?

89
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,000
The Ghost.

90
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,800
It's... It's the Ghost.

91
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,760
Just like in the serial murder case.

92
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,080
The Ghost has struck again.

93
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,120
Then tell me in detail

94
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,600
what happened.

95
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,200
My boss...

96
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,920
he has a drink around this time every night.

97
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:21,080
To-today, I prepared the drink

98
00:07:21,520 --> 00:07:22,960
and was going to take it to his office.

99
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:23,840
But...

100
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:26,080
I knocked, but no one answered.

101
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,160
I saw the door was unlocked,

102
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:28,760
so I went in myself.

103
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:29,560
Who knew...

104
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,480
my boss...

105
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:32,920
my boss was d-dead inside.

106
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:36,800
Show us.

107
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,400
Okay.

108
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:44,400
Don't be scared. Don't be scared.

109
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:12,040
The body has no obvious external injuries.

110
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,280
Over there.

111
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:23,720
Team Leader.

112
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:31,120
Of all times for something to happen...

113
00:08:36,160 --> 00:08:37,320
The victim's time of death...

114
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,480
...is likely more than two hours ago.

115
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,200
There's a pattern on this.

116
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:49,200
Shen Man.

117
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,400
Why are you here?

118
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,360
Get out, now.

119
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:52,760
Team Leader.

120
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,440
Right now, our superiors and the netizens...

121
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,600
...are putting so much pressure on us.

122
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:56,760
We need Shen Man...

123
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:58,520
...to help us steer public opinion.

124
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:10,360
You can't touch anything here.

125
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,560
It will contaminate the crime scene.

126
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:12,960
I know.

127
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,600
Also...

128
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:14,880
...anything you film...

129
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:16,600
...has to be reviewed by me first...

130
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,480
...before you can release it.

131
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:18,880
I understand.

132
00:09:22,160 --> 00:09:23,040
This seems...

133
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:24,720
...different from the scene of Ai Xia's death.

134
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:29,600
It is different.

135
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:34,560
These two patterns...

136
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:35,840
...can be pieced together.

137
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,040
But as for what the full pattern is...

138
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:39,800
...we'll have to find the other pieces.

139
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:41,440
Team Leader.

140
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:42,680
I suggest that this case...

141
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:44,520
...be merged with the Sang Tuo and Ai Xia case.

142
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:46,840
Wasn't that case already closed?

143
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,480
The pattern isn't complete yet.

144
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,520
This means the killer will likely...

145
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:50,800
...strike again, Team Leader.

146
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,000
Team Leader.

147
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:56,080
I'm heading back to the station now...

148
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:57,920
...to discuss this with the chief.

149
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,960
You guys go and investigate...

150
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:02,840
...the waiters here...

151
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:04,480
...and the gamblers who were present.

152
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:05,160
Yes, sir.

153
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:05,800
Yes, sir.

154
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,160
Pasin.

155
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:15,160
I'll handle the waiters.

156
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,640
The two of us will take the gamblers.

157
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:17,280
Okay.

158
00:10:17,560 --> 00:10:18,200
Let's go.

159
00:10:29,560 --> 00:10:30,320
What's wrong?

160
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:33,560
This office...

161
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:35,120
...doesn't have any security cameras.

162
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,320
Is there a registration list for the gamblers?

163
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,560
The people who come here to gamble...

164
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:40,840
...are all influential people.

165
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:42,600
Registering them...

166
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,880
...is indeed not very convenient.

167
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:47,120
You must at least have a list of people with gambling debts, right?

168
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,480
We do.

169
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,240
Lead the way.

170
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:56,600
You few were the ones on duty tonight.

171
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:00,320
While you were working today...

172
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,560
...did you notice anything unusual?

173
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,880
Don't be nervous, don't be nervous.

174
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:10,720
Just relax.

175
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:12,480
Officer Jiang isn't trying to suspect you.

176
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:14,200
It's just, have you recently...

177
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:15,960
...seen any suspicious people?

178
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:23,080
How long have you all been working here?

179
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:29,040
I think I've been working here the longest.

180
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,640
Almost a year and a half.

181
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:33,720
What, is this casino newly opened?

182
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:35,560
Not exactly.

183
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,720
It's just that before...

184
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:38,440
...the boss's father-in-law was running it.

185
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:40,400
After the boss's father-in-law died...

186
00:11:40,400 --> 00:11:41,560
...the boss reluctantly...

187
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:42,800
...took over this casino.

188
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,000
Reluctantly?

189
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:46,920
The boss has a very easygoing personality.

190
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:48,400
He's even a bit timid.

191
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:50,200
He's not really suited for this kind of business.

192
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,520
A lot of the casino's gambling debts...

193
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:52,680
...have become bad debts.

194
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:54,520
Then after Cheng Hui took over the casino...

195
00:11:54,800 --> 00:11:56,280
...why did he replace all the old employees?

196
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:57,760
It wasn't the boss...

197
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:59,520
...who replaced the previous employees.

198
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:01,400
It was...

199
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,720
...the old foreman.

200
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:06,120
He said this casino was haunted.

201
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:08,400
Then he insisted on leaving...

202
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:11,440
...and took all the previous employees with him.

203
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,800
When was the last time you saw the boss?

204
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:20,680
Not since the 29th of last month.

205
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:37,800
Good work.

206
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,200
Captain, this is yours.

207
00:12:41,680 --> 00:12:42,200
Yours.

208
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:43,080
Thanks.

209
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:43,840
This is yours.

210
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:44,400
Thanks.

211
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:50,600
As for the media,

212
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:53,120
I barely managed to keep them under control.

213
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:54,960
The Chief nearly chewed my head off.

214
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:56,840
Shen Man,

215
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:58,480
you need to highlight

216
00:12:58,480 --> 00:13:01,440
the diligence and hardships of our frontline officers.

217
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,080
I'll make sure of it.

218
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:05,360
Then I'll begin.

219
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:08,480
The previous crime and this current one...

220
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:10,840
the patterns can be pieced together,

221
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:12,040
but they are still incomplete.

222
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:14,520
Cheng Hui didn't know Su Nian or Anna.

223
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:16,840
He had no connection to Ai Xia or Sang Tuo either.

224
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:18,560
Why did the killer murder Cheng Hui?

225
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:24,760
Here.

226
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:26,680
What have you got?

227
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:32,720
A large amount of cash was found in Cheng Hui's mouth.

228
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:34,480
The throat mucosa was severely torn,

229
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:36,240
accompanied by bleeding and edema.

230
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:38,240
It's consistent with mechanical asphyxia.

231
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:39,160
Also,

232
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:40,520
I detected in his body

233
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:42,080
the same drug found in Sang Tuo and Ai Xia.

234
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:46,000
Cheng Hui took over

235
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:47,480
the Golden Elephant Casino a year and a half ago.

236
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:48,960
He was an honest man.

237
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:51,960
His employees spoke quite highly of him.

238
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:55,160
His character could even be described as cowardly.

239
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:57,680
He didn't seem like the type to offend anyone.

240
00:13:58,840 --> 00:14:00,840
Cheng Hui and his wife Lisa were married for six years.

241
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:02,080
They have a child over six years old.

242
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:03,560
The couple had a good relationship.

243
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:04,720
In addition,

244
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:06,640
Cheng Hui's phone records

245
00:14:06,640 --> 00:14:07,440
show nothing suspicious.

246
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:12,080
Have you located his family?

247
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:15,080
I called them.

248
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:18,880
As for the casino patrons,

249
00:14:18,880 --> 00:14:20,360
although we can't check every single one,

250
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:22,880
those with gambling debts

251
00:14:22,880 --> 00:14:23,880
have all been ruled out as suspects.

252
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:27,960
It's this situation again.

253
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:30,080
How should we investigate?

254
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:34,200
What's on your mind?

255
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:37,520
That Cheng Hui and his wife...

256
00:14:37,520 --> 00:14:38,680
had a good relationship.

257
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:40,120
Does that matter?

258
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:41,360
If their relationship was so good,

259
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:42,720
and Cheng Hui didn't come home all night,

260
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:44,840
why didn't his wife look for him?

261
00:14:46,680 --> 00:14:48,920
Mei Dong, are you sure you contacted Lisa?

262
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:52,520
I called her.

263
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:54,320
It didn't go through.

264
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,280
It didn't go through?

265
00:14:56,280 --> 00:14:57,560
Then go find her!

266
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:07,480
Sang Tuo and Ai Xia not only trafficked babies,

267
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:08,600
they also framed Anna

268
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:09,920
for killing an infant.

269
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:11,360
The talismans on the bodies

270
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:12,600
and the removed organs

271
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:13,880
simply record the crimes

272
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:14,960
they committed.

273
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:18,600
Are you saying that

274
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:21,400
Cheng Hui's death might be related to greed?

275
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:25,720
But Cheng Hui was weak and incompetent.

276
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:27,880
After taking over the casino,

277
00:15:27,880 --> 00:15:29,200
he lost so much money.

278
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:31,840
It really doesn't seem to have anything to do with greed.

279
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:34,640
Ai Xia, the miracle doctor who saved lives,

280
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:35,800
has also fallen from grace.

281
00:15:36,960 --> 00:15:38,160
It seems someone

282
00:15:38,160 --> 00:15:40,040
is truly living behind a mask.

283
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:43,800
Let's go.

284
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:47,160
Is anyone here?

285
00:15:51,720 --> 00:15:52,760
Is anyone here?

286
00:16:10,800 --> 00:16:12,440
Looks like no one's home today.

287
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:13,480
Let's go.

288
00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:22,840
There's someone inside.

289
00:16:23,480 --> 00:16:24,200
Keep walking.

290
00:16:49,640 --> 00:16:52,360
Happy birthday to me.

291
00:16:52,560 --> 00:16:54,880
Happy birthday to you.

292
00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:58,560
Happy birthday to me.

293
00:16:58,680 --> 00:17:01,760
Happy birthday to me.

294
00:17:13,320 --> 00:17:14,400
Officer.

295
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:15,920
I'm the nanny here.

296
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:17,880
It's my birthday today.

297
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:20,080
The Mister and Missus happen to be away.

298
00:17:20,080 --> 00:17:22,440
So I asked my boyfriend...

299
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:24,040
...to come celebrate with me.

300
00:17:28,360 --> 00:17:29,360
Lisa isn't home?

301
00:17:30,080 --> 00:17:31,640
The Missus took the child on a trip.

302
00:17:31,640 --> 00:17:32,920
It's been over a week.

303
00:17:33,520 --> 00:17:35,000
Do you know where they went?

304
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:36,400
I don't know.

305
00:17:38,960 --> 00:17:39,840
Officer.

306
00:17:39,840 --> 00:17:42,400
Is there a reason you're looking for the Missus?

307
00:17:42,680 --> 00:17:43,600
Cheng Hui is dead.

308
00:17:43,840 --> 00:17:45,080
We're here to notify the family.

309
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:47,000
Dead?

310
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:48,720
The Mister is dead?

311
00:17:49,400 --> 00:17:50,840
He was perfectly fine.

312
00:17:50,840 --> 00:17:51,760
How can that be?

313
00:17:56,080 --> 00:17:57,960
Did Cheng Hui and Lisa have a good relationship?

314
00:17:58,200 --> 00:18:00,000
The Mister doted on the Missus.

315
00:18:00,240 --> 00:18:01,680
They had a very good relationship.

316
00:18:06,480 --> 00:18:07,680
Can we take a look around?

317
00:18:09,080 --> 00:18:09,680
Go ahead.
